Dark brows, subtle floral patterns lie beneath the scars;
the undulating form resembles flowing water.
Through and through, a verdant spring emerges;
dark as green, dark as translucent green,
dark as translucent green with verdant hues.

Subtle brows, a veiled cultural presence;
Beneath the hurt of a prostrate son,
Wavy patterns resembling water;
A single sigh conveys the verdant spring,
Dark like green, dark like exhaling green,
Dark like exhaling charcoal green.
